### ========== PACIENTES ==========

### Obtener todos los pacientes
GET http://localhost:5154/api/Pacientes

### Crear un paciente
POST http://localhost:5154/api/Pacientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Juan",
  "apellido": "Pérez",
  "cedula": "12345678",
  "fechaNacimiento": "1990-05-15",
  "telefono": "555-1234",
  "email": "juan@email.com",
  "direccion": "Calle Principal 123",
  "numeroHistoriaClinica": "HC-001"
}

### Obtener un paciente específico
GET http://localhost:5154/api/Pacientes/1

### Actualizar un paciente
PUT http://localhost:5154/api/Pacientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "nombre": "Juan Carlos",
  "apellido": "Pérez García",
  "cedula": "12345678",
  "fechaNacimiento": "1990-05-15",
  "telefono": "555-9999",
  "email": "juancarlos@email.com",
  "direccion": "Avenida Principal 456",
  "numeroHistoriaClinica": "HC-001"
}

### Eliminar un paciente
DELETE http://localhost:5154/api/Pacientes/1

